      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WARM COCKLES (1) has missed the frame at his last couple but placed three back at Geelong and he does perform well at this trip. This looks easier and expected to bounce back. NIGEL DEVERE (2) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.5 lengths (27.49) behind Paw Cornelius at Horsham. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Hard to beat again. NANCY DEVERE (7) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 0.8 lengths (30.29) behind Greysynd Clyde at The Meadows. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Expected to feature. TIGER ROCKS (4) was in the money again last start when second at this track (34.49).",
